---
Regression for #481 under `--target workers`: a context that `uses` a commons
and calls a user-defined static method (`Cents.fromInt`) тАФ and an instance
method (`c.equals`) тАФ on one of the commons' refined types. The workers wrapper
emits the same rebranded const as the bundle target, so it must likewise forward
the commons' attached methods; before the fix the const carried only the
built-in `of`/`unsafe` and the calls failed `tsc`.
---
context api

uses money

service mk {
  on call(n: Int) -> Effect[Bool] {
    let r = Cents.fromInt(n)
    match r {
      Ok(c) => Effect.pure(c.equals(c))
      Err(_) => Effect.pure(false)
    }
  }
}
